text: Narystau () is a rural locality (a selo) in Ilchigulovsky Selsoviet, Miyakinsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 331 as of 2010. There are 3 streets. == Geography == It is located 54 km from Kirgiz-Miyaki, 5 km from Ilchigulovo. == References == Category:Rural localities in Miyakinsky District
title: Narystau
